results.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PS 'Seafoam'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PS ‘Seafoam’ updates the iconic silhouette with a two-tone palette geared for the warm weather months. The upper is constructed from clean white leather with contrasting nubuck overlays in a pale green finish. The same pastel hue is repeated on the signature Swoosh, Nike branded tongue tag and durable rubber outsole. Woven white laces are outlined in reddish bronze for an unexpected pop of contrasting color.

results.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Electro Orange'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS ‘Electro Orange’ features a familiar color palette that recalls the original ‘Shattered Backboard’ release from 2015. The high-top carries a white leather upper with contrasting black hits on the eyestay, forefoot overlay and nylon tongue, the latter embellished with a woven Nike Air tag. On the lateral ankle flap, the Jordan Wings logo is stamped in black, matching the signature Swoosh. Contrasting orange accents land on the padded collar and rubber outsole.

results.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro GS 'Racer Blue'
results.story: Offered in big kid sizing, the Air Jordan 3 Retro GS ‘Racer Blue’ is dressed in classic color blocking reminiscent of the OG ‘Fire Red’ colorway from 1988. Tumbled white leather is utilized on the upper, accented with dark grey elephant-print overlays at the toe and heel. Royal blue accents make their way to the sneaker’s molded eyelets, perforated leather collar and polyurethane midsole, enhanced with visible Air sole cushioning under the heel. The vibrant hue is repeated on Jumpman branding hits at the tongue and back heel.

results.name: Air Jordan 13 Retro Low GS 'Very Berry'
Jordan Delta 2 GS 'Thermo White'
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the Jordan Delta 2 GS ‘Thermo White’ highlights contrasting tones on a lifestyle silhouette that blends comfort, craftsmanship and a modern, deconstructed aesthetic. Powder blue suede and white textile make up the composition of the upper, reinforced with a rigid mudguard and a black nubuck toe wrap. On the lateral side, a bright red Jumpman tag is affixed to the decorative suede eyestay. Matching crimson hits land on the woven tongue tag and extended heel tab. The sneaker rides on a Cushlon foam midsole, reinforced underfoot by durable rubber in high-wear areas.

results.name: Air Jordan 7 Retro GS 'Flint' 2021
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 7 Retro GS ‘Flint’ brings back a 2006 colorway in big kid sizing. The mid-top makes use of a grey nubuck upper with white tumbled leather overlays and a Huarache-like inner sleeve for a snug, comfortable fit. Court Purple accents make their way to Air Jordan lettering on the tongue, an embroidered Jumpman on the lateral collar and a raised ‘23’ on the angular heel patch. The sneaker rides on a foam midsole with Nike Air cushioning in the heel for improved impact protection.

results.name: Air Jordan 7 Retro PS 'Flint' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Air Jordan 7 Retro PS ‘Flint’ revives a 2006 colorway for little kids. The outward design is true to the original, featuring an upper that combines grey nubuck with tumbled white leather. ‘Air Jordan’ is embroidered in purple lettering on the signature Air Jordan 7 tongue, connected to a Huarache-like inner sleeve and covered in a unique geometric print. Matching violet accents appear on a Jumpman logo on the lateral collar and a molded ‘23’ on the heel patch.

Travis Scott x Air Jordan 6 Retro PS 'British Khaki'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Travis Scott x Air Jordan 6 Retro PS ‘British Khaki’ delivers a refined take on the classic mid-top. Soft suede in a dark tan finish makes up the composition of the upper, equipped with a button stash pocket on the lateral collar and a zippered pouch on the medial side. A Jumpman icon in Bright Crimson stands out on the canvas tongue, matched by Nike Air and Cactus Jack logos on the heel of the left and right shoe. They’re joined by the Houston rapper’s personal branding hits on the medial-side midsole and semi-translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Crater Impact PS 'Light Bone Stone'
results.story: Developed for little kids, the Nike Crater Impact PS ‘Light Bone Stone’ features a lightweight build predicated on sustainability. The tan textile upper incorporates recycled fibers and reduced materials. The latter is achieved by using embroidered Swooshes and efficient overlays, including an orange webbing strap that folds in on itself to create lace loops. The sneaker rides on a powder blue Crater foam midsole with speckled sidewalls that indicate the inclusion of Nike Grind.

results.name: Crater Impact PS 'Summit White Grey Fog'
results.story: Offered in little kid sizing, the Nike Crater Impact PS ‘Summit White Grey Fog’ highlights a neutral palette on a sustainable sneaker made with recycled materials and efficient construction techniques. The latter is exemplified by embroidered Swooshes and eyelet webbing that folds in on itself to create lace loops. The sneaker’s off-white textile upper is mounted on a lightly speckled Crater Foam midsole that incorporates Nike Grind, composed of discarded rubber scraps from footwear manufacturing.

results.name: Star Wars x NMD_R1 Big Kid 'Rebels and the First Order'
Crater Impact GS 'Summit White Grey Fog'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Crater Impact GS ‘Summit White Grey Fog’ delivers a versatile sneaker designed with sustainability in mind. At least 20% recycled content goes into the lightweight build, featuring an off-white textile upper that incorporates recycled fibers. A tonal midfoot overlay provides added stability, while a bright orange webbing pull tab assists with easy on off. Plush cushioning is provided by a Crater Foam midsole made in part with Nike Grind.

results.name: Crater Impact GS 'Light Bone Stone'
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the Nike Crater Impact GS ‘Light Bone Stone’ showcases vibrant accents on a versatile low-top made with at least 20% recycled content by weight. Recycled fibers are woven into the tan textile upper, accented with embroidered Swoosh branding and equipped with orange webbing straps that form the lace loops. Nike Grind is built into the Crater Foam midsole, as well as the reinforced rubber placed under the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Air Zoom Pegasus 38 GS 'Black White'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 GS ‘Black White’ delivers an essential two-tone colorway of the performance runner. The lightweight upper is crafted from ventilated black mesh with a wider toe box and low-cut collar. A set of interior webbing straps are integrated into the laces, offering midfoot lockdown and a personalized fit. The sneaker sits atop a plush foam midsole, featuring an Air Zoom unit under the ball of the foot for responsive cushioning.

results.name: Court Borough Mid 2 GS 'Black Game Royal'
results.story: Offered in big kid sizing, the Nike Court Borough Mid 2 GS ‘Black Game Royal’ features an essential two-tone color scheme on a basketball-inspired sneaker built for playtime. The upper combines easy-to-clean leather and breathable mesh on the collar, equipped with a webbing pull tab and secured with an adjustable hook-and-loop strap for a custom fit. The mid-top is supported by durable cupsole tooling, complete with flex grooves built into the rubber outsole for a natural stride.

results.name: Air Force 1 Low GS 'Patriots'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Air Force 1 Low GS ‘Patriots’ gets dressed in a familiar color combination that recalls New England’s NFL franchise. The retro low-top utilizes a white tumbled leather upper with a cut-out navy Swoosh and red mini-Swooshes embroidered on the vamp and lateral forefoot. Additional branding hits land on an elongated woven tongue tag and an added pull tab at the heel. The sneaker is nestled atop a durable rubber cupsole, featuring encapsulated Nike Air cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Presto GS 'White Volt'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Presto GS ‘White Volt’ highlights a simplistic color scheme on a comfortable lifestyle runner originally billed as a T-shirt for feet. The lightweight build features a white mesh upper with a tonal midfoot cage and reinforced toe cap. Embroidered on the toe box is black Swoosh and ‘Just Do It’ in Volt lettering across the left and right shoe. Additional pops of Volt land on the heel and midsole, accented with five dots that nod to Nike’s short-lived Alpha Project initiative.

results.name: Jordan Zion 1 PS 'Gen Zion'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Jordan Zion 1 PS ‘Gen Zion’ represents the debut colorway of Zion Williamson’s first signature shoe. Black mesh is utilized on the upper, bolstered with a white synthetic overlay that wraps around the heel and extends to the midfoot, culminating in a ‘Z’ formation on the lateral side. Additional nods to the athlete take the form of an all-over ‘Zion’ print on the collar and a ZW logo stamped on the left tongue, complementing a matching gold Jumpman on the right. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a plush foam midsole, reinforced by a decoupled icy rubber outsole.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Glow In The Dark Insect Print'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘Glow in the Dark Insect Print’ is made for big kids with an abiding interest in entomology. The high-top utilizes a black canvas upper entirely plastered in a fluorescent green insect print that glows in the dark. Standard Chuck details remain intact, including chrome eyelets, winged tongue stitching and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. The sneaker sits atop a crisp white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes and a Converse-branded license plate.

results.name: Varsity Leather GS 'Particle Grey'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Varsity Leather GS ‘Particle Grey’ showcases a neutral monochromatic on a versatile everyday running shoe made with durability in mind. Grey leather is utilized on the upper, featuring tonal Swoosh branding and toe box perforations for improved ventilation. A classic Nike logo is pressed into the stitched tag that decorates the breathable mesh tongue. The low-top is mounted on a plush foam midsole, supported by lasting rubber in high-wear areas.

Air Max 90 PS 'White Hot Lime'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Air Max 90 PS ‘White Hot Lime’ adds vibrant accents to an otherwise neutral colorway of the retro runner. The upper foregoes traditional mesh construction in favor of an all-leather build, rendered in a soft grey finish with a contrasting black mudguard. Fluorescent green pops land on the signature Swoosh, Nike-branded heel patch and visible Max Air cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic waffled tread that ties back to Nike running heritage.

results.name: Jordan Zion 1 GS 'Gen Zion'
results.story: The Jordan Zion 1 GS ‘Gen Zion’ presents the launch colorway of Zion Williamson’s debut signature shoe in big kid sizing. Celebrating the athlete’s status as a generational talent, the mid-top carries a black mesh upper with a contrasting white synthetic overlay and a graffiti-like ‘Zion’ print throughout the padded textile collar. Gleaming pops of metallic gold land on branding elements that include a Jumpman icon on the right tongue, a ZW logo on the left, and ‘Zion’ inscribed on the heel tab. The sneaker rides on a full-length foam midsole, supported underfoot by an icy translucent rubber outsole.

X Ghosted.3 TF J 'Shock Pink'
results.story: Offered in kids sizing, the adidas X Ghosted.3 TF J ‘Shock Pink’ updates the turf shoe with a vibrant pink finish. The eye-catching hue is applied to a lightweight mesh upper that provides a snug, sock-like fit, thanks to the addition of a low-cut Clawcollar and a four-way stretch tongue. The streamlined build rides on a cushy EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged rubber outsole specifically designed for play on artificial-turf pitches.

results.name: X Ghosted.3 IN J 'Shock Pink'
results.story: An indoor soccer shoe made for kids, the adidas X Ghosted.3 IN J ‘Shock Pink’ features a highlighter finish designed to stand out on the pitch. The sock-like upper is constructed from coated mesh and equipped with a low-cut collar that wraps around the ankle without compromising mobility. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a full-length EVA midsole, reinforced by a grippy gum rubber outsole that offers superior traction on indoor surfaces.
